videos.headline: Jerome Ford powers forward for a Cincy TD
videos.description: Jerome Ford dives into the end zone to extend Cincinnati's lead over East Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jerome Ford powers forward for a Cincy TD) 2021/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alec Pierce makes an incredible TD grab for Cincy
videos.description: Desmond Ridder tosses a pass to the end zone and Alec Pierce jumps up to make a great play for another Bearcats touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Alec Pierce makes an incredible TD grab for Cincy) 2021/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincinnati runs a blocked field goal back for a TD
videos.description: Arquon Bush blocks the East Carolina field goal, then Ahmad Gardner scoops up the ball and runs it back for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincinnati runs a blocked field goal back for a TD) 2021/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincinnati completes 12-0 regular season with win at ECU
videos.description: Desmond Ridder tosses two touchdown passes as No. 4 Cincinnati beats East Carolina to finish the regular season undefeated.
